WEBVTT

1
00:00:09.027 --> 00:00:09.891
<i>C'mon!</i>

2
00:00:16.301 --> 00:00:18.895
<i>Running like a fugitive.</i>

3
00:00:19.904 --> 00:00:22.065
<i>Being chased by something</i>

4
00:00:23.741 --> 00:00:26.403
<i>Inside my heart is pounding</i>

5
00:00:27.512 --> 00:00:30.140
<i>My throat dry like it's withering</i>

6
00:00:31.849 --> 00:00:34.943
<i>For no single one.</i>

7
00:00:35.453 --> 00:00:38.718
<i>To none does belong.</i>

8
00:00:40.191 --> 00:00:44.457
<i>This time is ours. right now...</i>

9
00:00:47.098 --> 00:00:48.963
<i>Unraveling the pain.</i>

10
00:00:49.067 --> 00:00:50.796
<i>Unraveling our hearts.</i>

11
00:00:50.868 --> 00:00:53.200
<i>Unraveling shadows</i>

12
00:00:54.739 --> 00:00:56.502
<i>Stifling our breath.</i>

13
00:00:56.574 --> 00:00:58.474
<i>Reaching for beyond.</i>

14
00:00:58.543 --> 00:01:00.977
<i>Tearing through the dark</i>

15
00:01:02.880 --> 00:01:09.444
<i>In fighting and in love</i>

16
00:01:10.421 --> 00:01:13.049
<i>To the distant light above.</i>

17
00:01:13.491 --> 00:01:16.688
<i>Yes. we are on the way</i>

18
00:01:21.666 --> 00:01:23.031
<i>I wanna rock...</i>

19
00:01:25.436 --> 00:01:26.960
<i>Rockin' my heart</i>

20
00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:34.074
Do you want subtitles for any video?
-=[ ai.OpenSubtitles.com ]=-

21
00:01:42.149 --> 00:01:42.843
Hey. you!

22
00:01:43.383 --> 00:01:45.442
Are you sure you want
to look like that?

23
00:01:45.919 --> 00:01:47.887
Yes. of course!
C'mon! So hurry hurry!

24
00:01:49.389 --> 00:01:51.152
Don't regret it later.

25
00:01:52.092 --> 00:01:53.923
Say cheese!

26
00:01:56.363 --> 00:02:02.324
<i>My Name Is Konohamaru!</i>

27
00:02:17.884 --> 00:02:20.478
I couldn't decide on how to look.

28
00:02:20.821 --> 00:02:23.153
It took me 3 hours to decide.

29
00:02:23.457 --> 00:02:27.518
But as you can see.
it's more like a work of art.

30
00:02:27.594 --> 00:02:29.027
Doesn't it look great?

31
00:02:29.296 --> 00:02:30.490
Take it over.

32
00:02:30.697 --> 00:02:31.629
What?!

33
00:02:34.034 --> 00:02:35.296
Take it over.

34
00:02:35.936 --> 00:02:37.836
Stop saying that!

35
00:02:44.111 --> 00:02:44.770
Transform!

36
00:02:48.582 --> 00:02:51.050
Oh please. Lord Hokage...

37
00:03:06.032 --> 00:03:11.368
The Sexy Jutsu...
That's quite a devious technique.

38
00:03:13.673 --> 00:03:16.801
By the way Naruto.
where's your headband?

39
00:03:17.244 --> 00:03:20.680
I won't wear it until the orientation.
It might get scratched

40
00:03:21.748 --> 00:03:22.908
Well. that's just fine.

41
00:03:23.250 --> 00:03:27.619
But the Ninja Registration Form
is a very important document

42
00:03:27.754 --> 00:03:30.587
held in high regard by our village.

43
00:03:31.892 --> 00:03:34.360
Why do you want to look like this?

44
00:03:35.328 --> 00:03:36.454
Because!

45
00:03:36.530 --> 00:03:39.328
Anyway. how should I know
about all that stuff?

46
00:03:42.302 --> 00:03:44.236
Old man!
Get ready to fight!

47
00:03:45.772 --> 00:03:48.935
I am going to be the Fifth Hokage!

48
00:03:52.813 --> 00:03:54.678
Ouch!

49
00:03:55.649 --> 00:03:57.640
<i>If it's not one thing. it's another...</i>

50
00:03:59.953 --> 00:04:01.978
Drat! Is this a trap?

51
00:04:04.591 --> 00:04:07.617
Are you okay.
Honorable Grandson?

52
00:04:07.928 --> 00:04:10.089
May I just inform you that
there aren't any traps here...

53
00:04:10.497 --> 00:04:12.727
<i>Huh? What's with this runt?</i>

54
00:04:14.034 --> 00:04:14.500
What?!

55
00:04:15.101 --> 00:04:20.334
<i>I know this kid...</i>
<i>He's that Nine Tailed boy!</i>

56
00:04:20.674 --> 00:04:23.074
<i>He's a good for nothing scoundrel!</i>

57
00:04:23.543 --> 00:04:26.637
You must have done this to me!

58
00:04:27.347 --> 00:04:29.815
You tripped all by yourself. stupid!

59
00:04:30.016 --> 00:04:32.416
Hey! Let go of him!

60
00:04:32.719 --> 00:04:35.779
He is the Honorable Grandson
of the Third Hokage!

61
00:04:39.192 --> 00:04:42.025
<i>He stopped as soon as</i>
<i>he learned who I am...</i>

62
00:04:43.897 --> 00:04:46.058
<i>He's like my four eyed teacher.</i>

63
00:04:46.132 --> 00:04:47.861
He's just like everyone else!

64
00:04:48.468 --> 00:04:49.867
What's the matter?

65
00:04:49.936 --> 00:04:51.563
Weren't you gonna hit me. huh?

66
00:04:51.805 --> 00:04:54.330
Can't do it 'cuz
I'm the Hokage's grandson. eh?

67
00:04:54.407 --> 00:04:57.968
As if I care!
Imbecile!

68
00:05:00.513 --> 00:05:01.605
<i>This guy...</i>

69
00:05:03.516 --> 00:05:05.177
What?!

70
00:05:05.685 --> 00:05:07.550
<i>Good grief...</i>

71
00:05:10.523 --> 00:05:11.717
Listen to me.

72
00:05:11.791 --> 00:05:15.056
You are the Honorable Grandson
of the Third Hokage.

73
00:05:15.595 --> 00:05:21.363
Even though that scoundrel hit you.
you must not associate with his kind.

74
00:05:23.436 --> 00:05:26.462
Nothing good will come of
your tangling with him.

75
00:05:26.806 --> 00:05:29.001
This is your distinguished
teacher Ebisu.

76
00:05:29.075 --> 00:05:30.838
and I am never wrong
about these things!

77
00:05:31.578 --> 00:05:34.547
Don't you want to become
the Fifth Hokage?

78
00:05:35.215 --> 00:05:37.706
Then allow me
to teach you Ninjutsu.

79
00:05:37.784 --> 00:05:39.843
so that your dream will
become a reality.

80
00:05:40.287 --> 00:05:41.219
That's right.

81
00:05:41.288 --> 00:05:46.885
Stick with me and you will gain a shortcut
towards becoming the Fifth Hokage.

82
00:05:46.960 --> 00:05:49.690
Is that clear. Honorable Grandson?

83
00:05:53.466 --> 00:05:54.763
He's gone!

84
00:05:55.168 --> 00:05:58.194
It seems he's gone after Naruto.

85
00:05:58.271 --> 00:05:58.896
Oh no!

86
00:05:59.172 --> 00:06:00.196
This is terrible!

87
00:06:00.740 --> 00:06:02.207
Honorable Grandson!

88
00:06:03.843 --> 00:06:07.472
<i>How did he become like this?</i>

89
00:06:09.349 --> 00:06:13.149
<i>That was the 20th sneak attack today.</i>

90
00:06:14.321 --> 00:06:18.223
<i>And now he's in the company of Naruto.</i>
<i>I'm a bit worried.</i>

91
00:06:19.626 --> 00:06:23.392
<i>I just hope he doesn't pick up</i>
<i>more foolishness.</i>

92
00:06:38.411 --> 00:06:38.706
Huh?

93
00:07:05.405 --> 00:07:06.531
Stop following me!

94
00:07:06.673 --> 00:07:07.605
What is it now?!

95
00:07:10.810 --> 00:07:12.710
Your camouflage is pathetic.

96
00:07:17.851 --> 00:07:19.842
You've seen through my disguise...

97
00:07:19.919 --> 00:07:22.012
Your reputation is well earned.

98
00:07:23.590 --> 00:07:26.684
I will allow you to make me
your apprentice.

99
00:07:28.862 --> 00:07:31.831
But you must first teach me that
"Sexy Jutsu" technique

100
00:07:31.898 --> 00:07:33.957
you used to beat Grandpa Hokage.

101
00:07:34.701 --> 00:07:36.362
You gotta be kidding.

102
00:07:36.603 --> 00:07:39.231
I beg you to say yes. boss!

103
00:07:39.305 --> 00:07:40.067
Huh?

104
00:07:40.573 --> 00:07:41.301
Boss?

105
00:07:41.641 --> 00:07:44.109
Boss! Boss! Boss!

106
00:07:45.779 --> 00:07:47.474
I guess I have no choice.

107
00:07:51.284 --> 00:07:51.875
Listen.

108
00:07:52.285 --> 00:07:54.378
In order to become a skilled Ninja.

109
00:07:54.554 --> 00:07:56.988
you must first learn to
control your Chatora.

110
00:07:57.791 --> 00:07:58.416
Chatora?

111
00:08:02.228 --> 00:08:03.752
Yes. Chatora.

112
00:08:04.197 --> 00:08:06.927
Boss. I think you mean Chakra.

113
00:08:07.967 --> 00:08:08.934
Silence!

114
00:08:09.002 --> 00:08:10.469
That's what real Ninjas call it!

115
00:08:10.603 --> 00:08:12.901
Oh! I didn't know that!

116
00:08:14.774 --> 00:08:16.833
<i>Whew... I'm glad he's a fool.</i>

117
00:08:17.644 --> 00:08:20.010
Listen. Chakra essentially means...

118
00:08:20.246 --> 00:08:24.205
Basically. it is the energy needed
in order to use Jutsu.

119
00:08:24.317 --> 00:08:24.578
Huh?

120
00:08:25.085 --> 00:08:28.577
In other words. fundamentally Ninja Arts
combine the Chakra.

121
00:08:28.655 --> 00:08:32.523
the physical energy accumulated
from each cell in the body

122
00:08:33.159 --> 00:08:36.560
with spiritual energy intensified
through training and experience.

123
00:08:36.629 --> 00:08:40.156
This combined energy is summoned
with certain hand signs.

124
00:08:40.366 --> 00:08:41.594
You made me think
you knew all that.

125
00:08:41.668 --> 00:08:42.999
when you were just reading
from a scroll!

126
00:08:44.204 --> 00:08:46.900
Much has been said about
perfecting the Ninja techniques.

127
00:08:46.973 --> 00:08:49.942
but it really boils down
to just one thing.

128
00:08:50.477 --> 00:08:51.569
And what is that?

129
00:08:52.312 --> 00:08:53.870
Hard work and guts.

130
00:08:54.447 --> 00:08:56.210
Hard work and guts?

131
00:08:56.649 --> 00:08:57.411
That's right.

132
00:08:57.484 --> 00:09:00.282
So be ready for the challenging tasks
I will give you.

133
00:09:00.420 --> 00:09:01.887
Yes. boss!

134
00:09:02.188 --> 00:09:05.157
Good. Let's start right now.
Transform for me.

135
00:09:05.391 --> 00:09:05.880
Huh?

136
00:09:07.026 --> 00:09:10.393
Let me see first
how much you already know.

137
00:09:10.897 --> 00:09:13.457
But what do I transform into?

138
00:09:23.243 --> 00:09:25.507
OK... First. transform into that lady.

139
00:09:25.845 --> 00:09:27.676
An easy task. boss.

140
00:09:29.749 --> 00:09:30.408
Transform!

141
00:09:31.885 --> 00:09:33.978
Well. do I look like her?

142
00:09:38.558 --> 00:09:41.254
Uhm... Well. the clothes do and...

143
00:09:43.229 --> 00:09:44.628
And what's so similar
about that?!

144
00:09:45.832 --> 00:09:47.322
Honorable Grandson.

145
00:09:47.500 --> 00:09:50.936
If you will transform into me.
at least try to look a little cuter. OK?

146
00:09:52.939 --> 00:09:53.633
She's scary!

147
00:09:56.209 --> 00:09:58.871
Why am I the one who gets hit?

148
00:10:02.282 --> 00:10:05.649
OK!
Next. we'll do some research on sexiness!

149
00:10:05.718 --> 00:10:07.049
Yes. boss!

150
00:10:19.766 --> 00:10:23.998
I told you I don't allow
reading here. Naruto!

151
00:10:31.578 --> 00:10:35.878
This is the last test.
Put all of your effort into it!

152
00:10:35.949 --> 00:10:37.507
Yes. boss!

153
00:10:37.750 --> 00:10:38.239
Transform!

154
00:10:54.367 --> 00:10:56.426
Naruto! It's you again!

155
00:11:00.773 --> 00:11:02.263
Why is it always me...?

156
00:11:03.743 --> 00:11:04.334
Sorry.

157
00:11:04.544 --> 00:11:05.101
Huh?

158
00:11:05.612 --> 00:11:07.876
It's because
I'm the Hokage's grandson.

159
00:11:09.382 --> 00:11:10.940
Don't worry about it.

160
00:11:11.284 --> 00:11:11.773
Huh?

161
00:11:12.685 --> 00:11:15.677
You're now ready to perform
the Sexy Jutsu!

162
00:11:16.789 --> 00:11:19.155
You just need more practice.

163
00:11:22.328 --> 00:11:23.727
Yes. boss!

164
00:11:24.931 --> 00:11:27.456
OK. keep in mind...
the point is for "boom boom boom"!

165
00:11:27.834 --> 00:11:28.493
Now do it!

166
00:11:28.568 --> 00:11:30.934
Yes. boss!
Transform!

167
00:11:34.040 --> 00:11:35.905
What do you think?

168
00:11:38.111 --> 00:11:39.203
That won't do!

169
00:11:39.779 --> 00:11:41.406
More slender.

170
00:11:41.547 --> 00:11:42.605
Yes. boss!

171
00:11:43.349 --> 00:11:44.680
Is this okay?

172
00:11:45.618 --> 00:11:47.813
Not yet.
More attractive.

173
00:11:47.887 --> 00:11:48.979
Yes. boss!

174
00:11:49.622 --> 00:11:51.214
How about now?

175
00:11:54.694 --> 00:11:58.892
<i>That Naruto... What is he teaching</i>
<i>the Honorable Grandson...?</i>

176
00:12:00.733 --> 00:12:04.533
Where the hell could they be...?

177
00:12:05.538 --> 00:12:10.032
<i>I am a distinguished teacher</i>
<i>training potential Hokage.</i>

178
00:12:10.543 --> 00:12:15.571
<i>All those who interfere</i>
<i>will be eliminated.</i>

179
00:12:37.970 --> 00:12:38.959
You know I've been wondering...

180
00:12:39.038 --> 00:12:42.371
You seem obsessed with beating
your Grandpa Hokage.

181
00:12:45.778 --> 00:12:47.871
My name is Konohamaru.

182
00:12:48.815 --> 00:12:50.942
It was Grandpa who gave me
that name.

183
00:12:51.884 --> 00:12:53.545
He name d me after our village.

184
00:12:55.855 --> 00:12:59.313
It should be easy for everyone
here to remember.

185
00:12:59.859 --> 00:13:02.453
But nobody ever calls me
by that name.

186
00:13:03.696 --> 00:13:08.895
When they see me. all they see
is the grandson of Lord Hokage.

187
00:13:10.737 --> 00:13:13.638
No one sees me for who I really am.

188
00:13:14.307 --> 00:13:16.605
I can't stand it anymore.

189
00:13:17.176 --> 00:13:17.767
That's why...

190
00:13:19.178 --> 00:13:22.238
That's why I want the title
of Lord Hokage now.

191
00:13:25.852 --> 00:13:29.447
Idiot... Who do you think
will accept you. huh?

192
00:13:29.756 --> 00:13:30.279
Huh?

193
00:13:30.723 --> 00:13:34.181
You won't win the title
that easily. you know.

194
00:13:34.394 --> 00:13:35.088
What?!

195
00:13:36.429 --> 00:13:37.657
It's not that simple.

196
00:13:39.832 --> 00:13:43.427
If you're really serious about gaining
the title of Lord Hokage...

197
00:13:44.570 --> 00:13:45.537
What?

198
00:13:47.640 --> 00:13:50.074
You'll have to beat me first!

199
00:14:05.391 --> 00:14:09.054
Lord Hokage!
I've been looking for you.

200
00:14:09.595 --> 00:14:10.527
Iruka.

201
00:14:11.330 --> 00:14:15.061
Did Naruto re submit
his Ninja Registration Form?

202
00:14:15.635 --> 00:14:16.124
Yes.

203
00:14:16.536 --> 00:14:19.664
When I lectured to him the other night
at the ramen stand.

204
00:14:19.906 --> 00:14:24.070
he said he will make everyone accept him
now that he's a Ninja.

205
00:14:24.510 --> 00:14:26.375
He's been happy since then.

206
00:14:32.452 --> 00:14:36.980
It might not be easy for Naruto
to realize that dream.

207
00:14:37.323 --> 00:14:37.789
Huh?

208
00:14:38.758 --> 00:14:40.817
As you well know.

209
00:14:40.893 --> 00:14:46.024
only the villagers who fought
the Nine-Tailed Fox Spirit 12 years ago

210
00:14:46.432 --> 00:14:50.425
know that the monster is sealed
inside Naruto.

211
00:14:51.771 --> 00:14:55.332
I ruled that no one shall speak
about that incident.

212
00:14:55.408 --> 00:14:59.242
I have severely punished those
who have broken this rule.

213
00:15:00.179 --> 00:15:03.740
Now our children know nothing about it.

214
00:15:03.983 --> 00:15:06.975
That is the only positive
development for Naruto.

215
00:15:07.787 --> 00:15:12.918
Before the Fourth Hokage trapped
the monster and died.

216
00:15:12.992 --> 00:15:16.052
his last wish was for the villagers
to regard Naruto as a hero.

217
00:15:16.429 --> 00:15:17.225
A hero?

218
00:15:18.397 --> 00:15:22.697
The Fourth Hokage sealed the monster
into the navel of a newborn baby

219
00:15:22.768 --> 00:15:24.633
whose umbilical cord
had just been cut.

220
00:15:25.304 --> 00:15:28.068
As the receptacle
for the Nine Tailed Fox Spirit.

221
00:15:28.140 --> 00:15:30.506
Naruto saved the village.

222
00:15:31.110 --> 00:15:36.047
Unfortunately. the other villagers
don't see him like that.

223
00:15:36.749 --> 00:15:41.618
Some even say that Naruto is
the Nine Tailed Fox Spirit himself.

224
00:15:42.455 --> 00:15:50.260
Little by little. that attitude has been
passed down to their own children.

225
00:15:52.532 --> 00:15:55.228
Iruka.
Do you know?

226
00:15:55.801 --> 00:15:56.358
What. sir?

227
00:15:57.270 --> 00:16:01.604
When someone is hated and people refuse
to accept his existence.

228
00:16:02.108 --> 00:16:06.977
he sees it in the eyes
of the people around him.

229
00:16:14.120 --> 00:16:15.417
I have found you!

230
00:16:15.721 --> 00:16:16.312
Huh?

231
00:16:21.260 --> 00:16:22.420
<i>That Demon Fox!!</i>

232
00:16:24.564 --> 00:16:27.465
<i>That cold look!</i>
<i>It's always like that!</i>

233
00:16:28.868 --> 00:16:31.962
Honorable Grandson.
we have to go now.

234
00:16:32.238 --> 00:16:33.034
No way!

235
00:16:33.472 --> 00:16:37.067
I want to beat Grandpa right now
so I can win the title of Lord Hokage!

236
00:16:37.777 --> 00:16:38.766
Don't get in my way!

237
00:16:39.045 --> 00:16:43.141
A Hokage must first know about virtue.
honor. etiquette. wisdom. loyalty. faith.

238
00:16:43.215 --> 00:16:44.807
judgment. obedience
and all that.

239
00:16:45.151 --> 00:16:47.381
He must be skilled at more than
thousand techniques...

240
00:16:47.453 --> 00:16:48.010
And then...

241
00:16:49.121 --> 00:16:49.712
Transform!

242
00:16:53.893 --> 00:16:56.225
Take this! Sexy Jutsu!

243
00:16:59.165 --> 00:17:00.860
What?
It didn't work!

244
00:17:00.967 --> 00:17:04.528
What kind of a
disgraceful spell is that?!

245
00:17:05.104 --> 00:17:06.662
I am a gentleman!

246
00:17:06.939 --> 00:17:10.636
Such vulgar attacks
will never work on me!

247
00:17:11.978 --> 00:17:16.677
Honorable Grandson!
That rascal will only make you an imbecile!

248
00:17:17.817 --> 00:17:19.808
Stick with me and...

249
00:17:19.885 --> 00:17:23.150
you will gain a shortcut
towards becoming the Fifth Hokage.

250
00:17:23.356 --> 00:17:24.914
C'mon. let's go!

251
00:17:24.991 --> 00:17:25.889
No way!

252
00:17:26.492 --> 00:17:27.686
Shadow Clone Jutsu

253
00:17:34.734 --> 00:17:37.396
Wow!
Fantastic!

254
00:17:44.076 --> 00:17:45.703
Ha!
That's nothing.

255
00:17:46.212 --> 00:17:48.373
I am a distinguished teacher.

256
00:17:48.781 --> 00:17:51.011
I am not as weak as Mizuki.

257
00:18:06.565 --> 00:18:07.429
Boss...

258
00:18:12.438 --> 00:18:13.166
Transform!

259
00:18:13.406 --> 00:18:16.136
Transform!

260
00:18:21.347 --> 00:18:23.577
Oh. Master Ebisu...

261
00:18:33.759 --> 00:18:36.023
I call it "the Harem Jutsu"!

262
00:18:37.930 --> 00:18:42.060
He combined the Multiple Clones with
his own Sexy Jutsu.

263
00:18:42.735 --> 00:18:45.329
<i>That's another devious attack.</i>

264
00:18:45.738 --> 00:18:49.367
<i>I probably won't even survive that one.</i>

265
00:18:54.513 --> 00:18:58.916
I can't even beat that
four eyed teacher of mine!

266
00:18:59.118 --> 00:19:03.020
I want the title of Lord Hokage so badly!
I want to be recognized by everybody!

267
00:19:03.089 --> 00:19:03.987
But I keep failing.

268
00:19:05.057 --> 00:19:06.547
You think it's that easy?

269
00:19:06.792 --> 00:19:07.315
Huh?

270
00:19:08.494 --> 00:19:11.361
It's given only to the greatest Ninja
in the village.

271
00:19:11.697 --> 00:19:14.564
Everybody must learn to believe in you.

272
00:19:17.436 --> 00:19:19.597
I've been through a lot already.

273
00:19:20.473 --> 00:19:22.805
It's been one struggle after another.

274
00:19:23.943 --> 00:19:27.902
But after all that.
I found someone who accepts me.

275
00:19:28.881 --> 00:19:31.406
I had to go through a lot...
Just for one person.

276
00:19:33.018 --> 00:19:35.009
You had better push yourself.

277
00:19:35.521 --> 00:19:36.351
For what?

278
00:19:38.224 --> 00:19:43.161
The path of getting the title.
Lord Hokage. is a brutal one.

279
00:19:52.304 --> 00:19:55.205
There's no such thing as a shortcut.

280
00:20:00.412 --> 00:20:02.573
<i>If you're really serious about</i>
<i>attaining the title of Lord Hokage</i>

281
00:20:03.182 --> 00:20:05.207
<i>You'll have to beat me first.</i>

282
00:20:08.954 --> 00:20:12.651
Who do you think you are.
lecturing me like that?

283
00:20:13.993 --> 00:20:16.587
I won't be your apprentice anymore.

284
00:20:21.534 --> 00:20:24.662
From now on. you're my rival.

285
00:20:29.408 --> 00:20:33.435
Unfortunately for you.
tomorrow I graduate from the Ninja Academy.

286
00:20:34.180 --> 00:20:39.914
Still. I'll consider you an equal someday
when we fight for the title of Lord Hokage.

287
00:20:41.921 --> 00:20:45.448
Let's look forward to that. Konohamaru.

288
00:21:09.615 --> 00:21:15.019
<i>You still have a long way to go</i>
<i>to become a real Ninja.</i>

289
00:22:52.650 --> 00:22:56.416
Aaah! Why do I have to be in
the same group with Sasuke?

290
00:22:56.487 --> 00:22:57.886
The guy I hate the most?

291
00:22:58.355 --> 00:23:00.084
Sakura keeps saying
"Sasuke Sasuke Sasuke!"

292
00:23:00.157 --> 00:23:01.852
And doesn't even
pay attention to me!

293
00:23:01.925 --> 00:23:06.362
It makes me so mad!
I got it! I'm going to pull one on him!

294
00:23:06.563 --> 00:23:10.055
I'm not gonna let him be so cool
in front of Sakura!

295
00:23:11.068 --> 00:23:13.866
Next Episode:
"Sasuke and Sakura: Friends or Foes?"

296
00:23:13.937 --> 00:23:16.565
Watch my outstanding performance!

